{"tid":1814032,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"香港minecraft","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T14:53:51.000Z","uid":345317,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b322131b6a7a7119b0e3abf315f49f17372b5a","tid":1814032,"uid":345317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:55:52.000Z","msg":"以前細個成日想喺minecraft起啲真實世界嘅嘢<br />\n經過今次抗爭運動，我想 &lsquo;係時候將成個香港擺落minecraft入面&rsquo;<br />\nscale 係1：2 左右(包埋水 大約32000x25000; 香港係60km x 45km 倒)<br />\n成個file 18GB （只係得啲地同埋海同埋山同埋呢座嘢）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZSkxiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZSkxiN.png&h=d566d676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標係把未淪陷得曬嘅香港留個紀念，日後相信很多人會想離開+唔想返香港。<br />\n（整完之後，有機會變成一個adventure map，打黑警@@)<br />\n<br />\n不過我自己一個起就真係起到2047都未起完<br />\n所以我來問問巴打絲打們，有沒人願意幫手：<br />\n1）起嘢；<br />\n2）開server （我沒有資源 &amp; 唔識開）；<br />\n3）做一個texture pack；<br />\n或 4）宣傳？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家"},{"pid":"008db0ea8da9d5da4640e5dc4496dfdfb39e325b","tid":1814032,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d5d89e8a072d0f67e353d70639e99a2dd3d2bc","tid":1814032,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be0624b0bcb7d9d5768c399392319fefa7a749dd","tid":1814032,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:58:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51f13f468fbadb2619ed472e3248e96e139a6906","tid":1814032,"uid":230777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:48:15.000Z","msg":"推，想幫手可以點？"},{"pid":"e5b0d7e9a22bcdbf312b4eda8ec0ee9bc100953f","tid":1814032,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:49:09.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff0ed98e0e93